{"tid":673859,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【貿易戰停火】WSJ：美國將取消銷售禁令 中興：消息屬實","createTime":"2018-05-22T07:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-22T08:12:20.000Z","uid":66271,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5598bb1cf7ee324cb2db7f01c8e87ba48743d9","tid":673859,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T07:59:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180522/58222991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F58222991&d=v1TkUrlo%2B04KWALS5dTm4DACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=0b6e5bad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180522%2F58222991&h=c3e215eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180522/58222991</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180522/large/1526963084_4950.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180522%2Flarge%2F1526963084_4950.jpg&h=553ac2b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》引述消息人士指，美中兩國就解決中興通訊爭端達成共識，美國將取消中興通訊銷售禁令，但中興將被要求大規模調整管理層及董事會。<br />\n據《每日經濟新聞》指，對更換管理層一事，中興方面回應：消息屬實。中美日前同意貿易戰暫停，中國將大量增加自美國的進口商品及服務等，以減少美對華的貿易逆差。<br />\n這場中美貿易戰始於3月22日，美國總統特朗普針對中國「經濟侵略」簽署備忘錄，對一百多種商品徵收關稅，涉及逾數百億美元。中國隨即反擊，提出向美國入口中國約30億美元的貨品徵收關稅。一場貿易戰隨即爆發，環球股市受壓。<br />\n中美貿易戰持續升溫，上月中，中興因違反美國制裁禁令，美國商務部在宣布對中興實施七年禁制令，禁止美國企業向中興出售零部件產品，令中興業務進入「休克」狀態。<br />\n及至上周貿易戰終於出現緩解跡象，繼月初美國財長姆欽率團訪華，與副總理劉鶴就兩國經貿問題進行磋商，及後劉鶴赴美訪問，這輪中美經貿磋商，雙方最大的共識和成果是通過協商妥善解決兩國經貿領域的問題，避免相互加徵產品關稅。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛三 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5fa32ace7763018c712e1acd9683e4c86686f1","tid":673859,"uid":58911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:09:58.000Z","msg":"布神睇聽日高開定低開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef7c93fd4d3fa3fb8136e18403fffd1940f61be0","tid":673859,"uid":31511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T08:12:20.000Z","msg":"tmr 2352<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}